review_blob: This is a delicious beer with notes of citrusy mosaic hops. Worth every penny. Purchased at binnys in Illinois.

Dark black pour with tan head. Aroma mild considering "hopped up" due to roasted malt character. Taste is piney with strong roast flavor, great strength in beer. VERY full on body/mouthfeel. Batch#277 278... Thank you sirs.
